column5: With the lady opening this weekend,Im sure there will be plenty out there fishing away. Hope monday brings lots of reports and smiles and photos anyway ya want.  Chillax and play safe out there all.
ill have a better weekend when division 19 opens next week have fun out there and paly safe looking forward to some bigguns be caught and photographed
Looks like its going to be a sweet weekend fishing and weather wise.  Have fun all.  See you'll out on the water  Joey
Well unfortunately I will be taking a weekend off of fishing but come the following I will be in paradise for a whole week.  Good Luck to those that get out this weekend!  Whopper
best of luck! I am looking forward to throwing my first line of 2007 out sunday morning
got the whole weekend off!!! looking forward to a great weekend of fishing and sun rays and most of important, relaxation..    . Hope you all have a great weekend as well ... Bud
Cant go....it sucks.... good luck everyone!

Have a great and safe weekend everyone. I have to help get 40 or so boats in the water at the club tomorrow so the best I can do is fish from 5PM or so Saturday till nightfall. Might even find a walleye or two.
